##  Task A-1: Assessor Selection

Weâ€™ve entered the **Assess** phase of the NIST Risk Management Framework, and Day 57 focuses on the foundational step: **choosing the right assessor**. After designing, implementing, and documenting controls for OpenMRS-on-AWS, itâ€™s time to invite an **independent, qualified professional** to evaluate the system.

This post walks through not just how to select an assessor, but how to **think like a leader** â€” making risk-informed, ethics-rooted, and collaborative choices that strengthen both compliance and culture.

